WEBVTT

00:00:59.807 --> 00:01:05.187
The thrill of archaeological discovery
is as powerful as love,

00:01:05.211 --> 00:01:10.258
because ancient history is the most
seductive mistress imaginable.

00:01:11.116 --> 00:01:13.419
Many archaeologists
have devoted their lives

00:01:13.443 --> 00:01:15.872
to unraveling the mysteries of the past

00:01:15.896 --> 00:01:17.552
under hot suns

00:01:18.585 --> 00:01:20.039
and Arctic winds

00:01:20.550 --> 00:01:22.428
and in dense rainforests.

00:01:23.518 --> 00:01:24.996
Many seek.

00:01:25.020 --> 00:01:26.171
Some discover.

00:01:26.195 --> 00:01:29.013
All worship at the temple of possibility

00:01:29.037 --> 00:01:31.857
that one discovery might change history.